OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FA coroner has ruled that gambling
OL,7,Faddiction played "a major part" in a
OL,8,Fman's death in Croydon.
OL,10,FGareth Evans, 40, took his own life in
OL,11,F2021 after withdrawing tens of
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds for in store
OL,13,Fbetting.
OL,15,FHis family say his death "was directly
OL,16,Fcaused by the gambling industry".
OL,26,@oD@ROUoD@_O]wD@ZOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
