CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FThe parent company of William Hill,
OL,7,Fwhere Gareth gambled, insists "it is
OL,8,Ffully committed to providing a safe
OL,9,Fand sustainable environment for all
OL,10,Fcustomers".
OL,12,FGareth was described by his family as
OL,13,Fa happy, popular person who loved
OL,14,Ffootball, pub quizzes and travel.
OL,16,FBut for 10 years he struggled with
OL,17,Fgambling and, in a note to his family,
OL,18,Fhe said it had caused him to suffer
OL,19,F"every day".
OL,26,@oD@_OUrD@JO]{D@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
