OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FGareth began online gambling on sports
OL,7,Fbut had to seek help to clear debt
OL,8,Ffrom his parents.
OL,10,FHe eventually barred himself from
OL,11,Fonline gambling after the issue re-
OL,12,Fsurfaced during lockdown.
OL,14,FHowever, in the six months before his
OL,15,Fdeath he withdrew #35,000 to bet in
OL,16,Fstore.
OL,18,FIn a note for his family, he wrote:
OL,20,F"I suffer every day. I started
OL,21,Fgambling and lost everything and more.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,F"I can't help but return to this
OL,7,Fdisgusting habit. I'm ashamed and I'm
OL,8,Fembarrassed.
OL,10,F"I've done nothing but gamble for six
OL,11,Fmonths. I lie to you daily and hate
OL,12,Fmyself for it."
OL,14,FOn Thursday, the coroner at Croydon
OL,15,FCoroners Court listed 'gambling
OL,16,Fdisorder' and 'depression' as
OL,17,Funderlying causes for Gareth's death.
OL,19,FThe coroner also criticised William
OL,20,FHill, where Gareth gambled, and the
OL,21,Fwider industry.
OL,26,@tD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
