PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FShe said: "The controls and support
OL,7,Fare in my view inadequate and measures
OL,8,Fneed to be improved...measures are
OL,9,Ffragmented and not standardised."
OL,11,FOutside court Tony Evans, Gareth's
OL,12,Fdad, spoke about their loss.
OL,14,FTony said:
OL,16,F"Four and a half years since Gareth
OL,17,Ftook his own life the coroner's
OL,18,Finvestigation has confirmed what we as
OL,19,Fa family always knew.
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@aO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,F"Namely that his death was directly
OL,7,Fcaused by the gambling industry and
OL,8,Ftheir dangerously addictive products.
OL,10,F"And William Hill failed in their
OL,11,Fduties to protect him. We are also
OL,12,Fpleased to see that the coroner
OL,13,Fintends to issue a prevention of
OL,14,Ffuture deaths report.
OL,16,F"Gambling had a catastrophic effect on
OL,17,FGareth's mental health.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1783774107
OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,F"He was a normal, happy and healthy
OL,7,Fperson. He had a good job and lots of
OL,8,Ffriends. He loved football, pub
OL,9,Fquizzes and travel.
OL,11,F"Although nothing can change what
OL,12,Fhappened to our wonderful Gaz we hope
OL,13,Fthis inquest can help us understand
OL,14,Fthat gambling kills."
OL,16,FWilliam Hill gave evidence at the
OL,17,Finquest about how they had made
OL,18,Fsweeping changes to improve safety
OL,19,Ffeatures and spot high-risk gamblers.
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
