OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FIn a statement William Hill's parent
OL,7,Fcompany said:
OL,9,F"We would like to extend our sincere
OL,10,Fcondolences to Mr Evans' family in
OL,11,Fthis tragic case.
OL,13,FSafer gambling is at the core of
OL,14,FEvoke's business, and we are fully
OL,15,Fcommitted to providing a safe and
OL,16,Fsustainable environment for all
OL,17,Fcustomers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
