OL,3,CGambling addiction played 'major part'
OL,4,Cin man taking own life, rules coroner
OL,6,FSince taking ownership of William Hill
OL,7,Fin July 2022, we have continuously
OL,8,Fevolved and improved our safer
OL,9,Fgambling processes and systems to
OL,10,Fensure we adhere to changing industry-
OL,11,Fwide regulations."
